title: Fypon FSR103X17 102 1/8"W x 16 13/16"H x 3/4"P, Round Fish Scale Panel, Woodgrain/Stainable
features: An easy way to enhance the look of your home
Fully primed and ready for paint

description: Our diverse selection of ornamental accents includes the round fish scale panel. Fish scale singles are a classic addition to the Victorian home. Additional decorative details, such as gable pediments, porch brackets, arches and spandrels are often used together to brings out the ornamental potential in the exterior. The fish scale panel is crafted in Urethane and detailed with a realistic wood grain texture and natural hue. The panel offers a cost-effective, durable and easy-to-install alternative to real wood shingles. The panel can also be stained like wood with realistic results. The fish scale panel is precision-molded and non-porous, so it will resist peeling, staining and decay.
